	<content><![CDATA[

vrrp is an open standard protocol to provide gateway redundancy for end clients.

it uses multicast 224.0.0.18 for sending hello packets.
it uses IP protocol 112.
if we have 3 routers in vrrp group, then one will be master, other two will be backup.


